product_name: Keen Durand Mid WP Hiking Boots - Women's
long_description: American built and ready to go right out of the box, the women's waterproof Keen Durand Mid WP Hiking Boots let you hit the trails whether the sun is shining or the rain clouds are hovering overhead. Waterproof nubuck leather and breathable mesh uppers have KEEN.DRY(TM) waterproof, breathable membranes to keep your feet dry on wet and muddy trails. Integrated polyurethane heel cushions and midsoles keep your feet comfortable during long days on the trail. Removable dual-density footbeds offer additional support and cushioning. Thermoplastic urethane shanks provide good stability for hiking on rugged trails. Grippy dual-compound rubber outsoles provide great traction. Keen Durand Mid WP Hiking Boots are assembled in the USA of imported and domestic materials.
